---
title: Chicken, Leek & Bacon Pie with Thyme & Mash Topping
description: We think the world's a better place when there's chicken pie for dinner! With a garlic and herb-seasoned bacon and leek filling and heavenly mashed potato topping (which the kids can help out with), this is just what we all need right now.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chicken-bacon-pie-f748a467.jpg
